comment: Baynes (DET) obtains a legal guarding position and jumps vertically contesting the driving shot attempt by LeVert (BKN).
Smith (DET) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with LeVert (BKN) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Lopez (BKN) sets the screen on Caldwell-Pope (DET) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Lopez (BKN) makes marginal contact with Baynes (DET) that does not affect his FOM.
[Detectable with stop watch] Baynes (DET) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Baynes (DET) sets the screen on LeVert (BKN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harris (DET) makes marginal contact with Lin (BKN) on his driving shot attempt.
Baynes (DET) and Lin (BKN) make incidental contact with one another following the shot attempt.
LeVert (BKN) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Morris (DET) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
The ball is last touched by Morris (DET) prior to going OOB.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of DET possession is overturned and BKN is awarded possession.
Baynes (DET) blocks the shot attempt by LeVert (BKN).
Harris (DET) and Hollis-Jefferson (BKN) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of DET possession is confirmed.
Baynes (DET) firms up his position and sets the screen on Dinwiddie (BKN).
Lin (BKN) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Baynes (DET).
Baynes (DET) legally contests Lopez' (BKN) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Hollis-Jefferson (BKN) and Harris (DET) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Dinwiddie (BKN) commits a take foul on Caldwell-Pope (DET).
LeVert (BKN) commits a take foul on Harris (DET).
Caldwell-Pope (DET) deflects the ball away from Lin (BKN).
Lin (BKN) commits a take foul on Morris (DET).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Hamilton (BKN) released his 3pt field goal prior to time expiring is confirmed.
